      { heading: "Yacht Party Music and Entertainment Options", content: "Music transforms a yacht charter into a party. The standard Bluetooth sound system lets you play your own playlists through the yacht's speakers — create a Spotify or YouTube Music playlist in advance. For an elevated experience, add-on entertainment options include: a professional DJ with their own equipment (€300–500) — ideal for dance parties with lighting effects; a live saxophonist or violinist (€200–350) — perfect for elegant atmospheres; a live band (€500–1000) — for larger yachts with space for performers; or a traditional Turkish musician with saz or oud (€200–300) — for cultural experiences. Many guests combine options: a live musician for the dining hour transitioning to a DJ for the dance portion. The yacht's sound system supports both indoor and outdoor speakers, so music flows throughout the vessel." , expertQuote: { text: "Boğaz'da parti organizasyonu, mekan ve atmosfer açısından rakipsiz bir deneyim sunar. Açık hava, su yüzeyi ve İstanbul manzarası her etkinliği özel kılar.", author: "Elif Korkmaz", title: "Yat Turizmi Danışmanı, TURSAB Üyesi" }},
      { heading: "Catering and Drinks for Yacht Parties", content: "Food and drinks are central to any great party. For yacht parties, several catering approaches work well. The meze and grill spread — a classic Turkish party menu with hummus, ezme, börek, grilled meats, and salads — is crowd-pleasing and easy to serve. A cocktail party format with canapés, finger foods, and a premium bar works well for networking-style events. A sit-down dinner is possible on larger yachts for more formal celebrations. Dessert-focused spreads with a custom cake, baklava, Turkish delight, and fruit are popular for birthdays. For drinks, the Premium package includes wine, beer, and spirits. The VIP package adds champagne and premium cocktails. You can also bring your own beverages on the Essential package. Non-alcoholic options including fresh juices, Turkish tea ceremony, and mocktails ensure everyone is included." },
      { heading: "Yacht Party Decoration and Setup Ideas", content: "Decorations transform a yacht into a party venue. MerrySails offers decoration packages including: balloon arches and balloon walls (solid colors, ombre effects, or themed), LED string lights for evening atmosphere, custom banners ('Happy Birthday', 'She Said Yes', company logos), flower arrangements (fresh roses, orchids, seasonal flowers), table centerpieces, photo backdrop walls for Instagram-worthy shots, confetti cannons for dramatic moments, and themed props. For birthdays, personalized number balloons and cake table setups are popular. For bachelorettes, rose gold accessories and custom sashes add to the fun. All decorations are set up before your arrival so the yacht is party-ready when you board. Cleanup is handled by the crew after the charter." , expertQuote: { text: "Özel yat kiralama, Boğaz deneyimini tamamen kişiselleştirme imkânı tanır. Rota, zamanlama ve servis tamamen misafirlerin tercihine göre şekillenir — bu esneklik başka hiçbir tur seçeneğinde yok.", author: "Burak Şahin", title: "Profesyonel Yat Kaptanı, 20 Yıllık Deneyim" }},
      { heading: "Planning Your Perfect Yacht Party", content: "A successful yacht party requires coordination. Start planning 1–2 weeks in advance: (1) Set your date, time, and guest count. (2) Choose your package (Essential €280, Premium €380, or VIP €680). (3) Select your theme and decoration preferences. (4) Choose add-ons (DJ, musician, photographer, special decorations). (5) Plan the food and drink menu. (6) Create your playlist or book entertainment. (7) Send invitations with marina directions and dress code. MerrySails handles all logistics — you focus on enjoying the party. Share your Pinterest board or Instagram inspiration and we match the vision. Group payments can be split among guests — a €380 Premium charter split among 12 friends is about €32 per person for a private yacht party on the Bosphorus." }
