      { heading: "Booking for Corporate Events", content: "Corporate yacht events benefit from advance planning. Book 2–4 weeks ahead and specify: event type and objectives, guest count and composition, preferred date and time (sunset events are most impressive), catering style and dietary requirements, AV/technical needs, branding requirements, and budget range. MerrySails provides a detailed event proposal including timeline, menu options, setup description, and itemized pricing. Corporate invoicing with company details is available. For recurring events (quarterly team celebrations, annual client entertaining), preferred rates can be arranged. The per-person cost of a yacht corporate event often compares favorably to upscale restaurant dining while delivering a far more memorable and impactful experience." }
