      { heading: "Booking Timeline for Groups", content: "Group bookings require more lead time than individual reservations. 4+ weeks ahead: Large groups (30+), corporate events, and wedding-related cruises. 2–3 weeks: Medium groups (15–30) during peak season. 1–2 weeks: Small groups (10–15) during off-peak. Day-of: Rarely possible for groups, as vessel allocation and catering require advance planning. For corporate events requiring AV equipment, branded materials, or specific entertainment, start planning 4–6 weeks ahead. Share your preliminary requirements early — even before finalizing guest count — so MerrySails can reserve appropriate vessels and resources." }
